    <detaileddescription>
<para>Abstract class for plugins All plugins MUST have this class as their parent and may implement any/all the callbacks marked <computeroutput>virtual</computeroutput> here.</para>
<para>/////For an example of a basic plugins see plugins/skeleton.h</para>
<para>Return value of callbacks: returning true to any of the callbacks tells <ref refid="classMR_1_1Viewer" kindref="compound">Viewer</ref> that the event has been handled and that it should not be passed to other plugins or to other internal functions of <ref refid="classMR_1_1Viewer" kindref="compound">Viewer</ref> </para>
    </detaileddescription>
